<LanguageData>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>questDescription->来自 [asker_nameFull] 的 [asker_faction_leaderTitle]、[asker_faction_name] 的紧急信息：“我们收到紧急情报，袭击者正在计划对我们的一个[settlement]发起协同攻击。那里的定居者毫无防备——大多数是农民、商人和家庭，只是想在荒地中生存。我们需要经验丰富的战士到达定居点，并在攻击开始之前帮助保卫它。”</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>questDescription->来自 [asker_nameFull] 的 [asker_faction_name] 的优先警报：“一个臭名昭著的袭击团伙被发现正在向 [settlement] 移动。那里的平民没有受过军事训练，武器也有限 - 他们只是坐以待毙。情报显示袭击者正在寻找定居点的食物储备和燃料储备。时间至关重要 - 在荒地秃鹫到来之前到达那里并加强防御。”</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>questDescription->来自 [asker_faction_name] 的求救信号：“[asker_nameFull] 这里。在收到有关该地区袭击者活动的报告后，我们与 [settlement] 失去了联系。我们的侦察兵表明，一场重大袭击即将发生 - 可能在几小时内。定居点居住着数十名无辜的幸存者，他们在这片被遗弃的荒地上建造了一些像样的东西。他们应该有机会保留他们辛辛苦苦建造的东西。”</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.3>questDescription->来自[asker_nameFull]、[asker_faction_leaderTitle]的紧急通讯：“袭击者已经像秃鹰一样在[settlement]盘旋了好几天，测试他们的防御能力。定居点几乎没有武装——他们是和平的人们，在废墟s中成功地开创了生活。有消息称袭击者计划在黎明时袭击他们。这些人在我们一无所有的时候把我们带走了——现在轮到我们支持他们了。”</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.3>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.4>任务描述->来自 [asker_faction_name] 的关键任务简报：一支全副武装的袭击者战队正在向 [settlement] 集结。该目标具有重要的战略意义——它位于主要贸易路线上并拥有清洁的水源。如果它倒塌，它将嵌入老旧en 该地区的每个掠夺团伙。 [asker_nameFull] 亲自请求援助：“帮助我们保护这些人。在这片荒原上，每一个正常运作的定居点都是希望的灯塔。”</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.4>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.0>任务名称-&gt;保卫[settlement]</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.1>任务名称-&gt;行动：保护[settlement]</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.1>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.10>结算-&gt;交易站</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.10>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.11>定居点->农业社区</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.11>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.12>定居点-&gt;边境定居点</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.12>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.13>定居点-&gt;难民营</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.13>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.14>定居点-&gt;拾荒者前哨站</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.14>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.15>定居点-&gt;平民定居点</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.15>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.2>任务名称-&gt;荒地防御：[settlement]</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.3>任务名称-&gt;围攻下的定居点</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.3>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.4>任务名称-&gt;[settlement]看台</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.4>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.5>任务名称-&gt;保护无辜者</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.5>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.6>任务名称-&gt;消除入侵者威胁</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.6>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.7>任务名称-&gt;在[settlement]进行最后一战</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.7>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.8>定居点-&gt;荒地定居点</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.8>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.9>定居点-&gt;幸存者前哨站</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.questNameRules.rulesStrings.9>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.0.name>定居者积分</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.0.name>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.elseNode.node.nodes.1.label>强盗袭来！</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.elseNode.node.nodes.1.label>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.elseNode.node.nodes.1.text>掠夺者战队已抵达定居点周边！枪响了——攻击开始了！</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.elseNode.node.nodes.1.text>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.node.nodes.1.label>袭击者袭击定居点！</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.node.nodes.1.label>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.node.nodes.1.text>荒野败类已经开始进攻了！定居点的守卫者正在为自己的生命而战 - 进入那里并帮助他们赶走这些袭击者！</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.node.nodes.1.text>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.0.node.nodes.0.customLetterLabel>和解防御成功</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.0.node.nodes.0.customLetterLabel>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.0.node.nodes.0.customLetterText>袭击者已被击退，定居点得以确立！心存感激的幸存者正在筹集他们能剩下的一切，作为你们英勇保卫家园的报酬。</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.0.node.nodes.0.customLetterText>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.0.node.nodes.0.nodeIfChosenPawnSignalUsed.label>[asker_faction_royalFavorLabel]</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.0.node.nodes.0.nodeIfChosenPawnSignalUsed.label>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.0.node.nodes.0.nodeIfChosenPawnSignalUsed.text>这些殖民者参与了任务[resolvedQuestName]的胜利。 [asker_definite] 想知道谁应该获得此服务的 [royalFavorReward_amount] [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel]。</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.0.node.nodes.0.nodeIfChosenPawnSignalUsed.text>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.1.label>结算超支</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.1.label>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.1.text>The raiders have overwhelmed the settlement's defenses. Smoke rises from the 废墟s as the survivors flee into the wasteland. Your mission has failed.</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.6.node.nodes.1.text>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.0.label>定居点被袭击者夺走</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.0.label>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.0.text>在没有援助的情况下，定居点陷入了袭击者的袭击。荒原上又一盏灯已经熄灭。任务 [resolvedQuestName] 失败。</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.0.text>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.16.node.nodes.0.label>定居点被掠夺者遗弃</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.16.node.nodes.0.label>
  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.16.node.nodes.0.text>如果你让定居点不设防，你就决定了它的命运。掠夺者在荒地取得了又一次胜利。</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.16.node.nodes.0.text>
</LanguageData>
